{
  "stem": "20616.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't even think it was relevant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When-- after World War II, you know there was a lot of disillusionments here and a friend of mine talked me into coming to a meeting where Hitler spoke.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he signed up as a supporter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He felt-- I thought it was kind of stupid what he said.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said, can I put your name down?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said, oh, I'm not really into it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Let me put my name down-- so-- put your name down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he went to one or two more meetings and he said after that, he said it was such nonsense he never even thought of attending another meeting.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So you have to be careful sometimes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Sometimes it can-- you know, I was only 20 years old and I was not the most knowledgeable person in the world, but I learned very quickly and I had to learn very quickly and I had to make decisions which affected people's lives and I had to be conscious of it and it affected people's careers and reputations and so on.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And later on, we got rid of-- we had to screen all the prospective officials of the-- of the-- of the government.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The mayors have to be-- have to be-- there were no elections, they have to be appointed and officials have to-- had to be appointed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we also got-- it was terrible at that time-- denunciations where people denounced each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He did this and this and he did that and-- and-- and he shouldn't be appointed and he doesn't deserve to be appointed and somebody else should be.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, of course, nobody was a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the most terrible area where Nazism flourished earliest on.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
